# @description: Materializes the "Provenance Stratum". Injects forensic trace 
#               headers into all forged scriptures, chronicling the logic gates 
#               and variables used in their alchemical creation.
# @category: Velm-Core / Forensics
# @vibe: debugging, transparency, logic-trace, provenance, audit, forensics
# @provides: [forensic-trace-service, provenance-authority, debug-scribe]
